A serene Japanese garden at twilight in Studio Ghibli style, featuring three ancient stone statues arranged in a triangular formation around a small empty pedestal. Each statue depicts a robed monk in a different pose: one reaching upward with open hands, one sitting with arms crossed in refusal, and one in perfect stillness with palms resting on knees in deep meditation. Soft fireflies drift through the scene, casting gentle golden light across a reflecting pond filled with lotus flowers. Cherry blossom petals float on a gentle breeze. The sky transitions from deep purple to soft pink, with a crescent moon visible through wispy clouds. Moss-covered rocks and delicate bamboo frame the peaceful scene.
